%e A079729 Sequence begins: 1,2,2,3,3,1,1,1,2,2,2,3,1,2,3,3,1,1,... read it as: (1),(2,2),(3,3),(1,1,1),(2,2,2),(3),(1),(2),(3,3),(1,1),... then count the terms in parentheses to get: 1,2,2,3,3,1,1,1,2,2,... which is the same sequence.
